node.text: A quick ride off the shores of Miami is beautiful Bimini, an island I hold close to my heart. Filmed this three years ago & finally brought it to life. Leave your feedback in the comments! 🤙 This mystic, gorgeous & historical island has been loved by everyone from Ernest Hemingway to Martin Luther King Jr. For those who love tropical vibes, adventure, & culture - this island must go on your bucketlist! 🐬 Id love your support! Don’t forget to share this video, tag friends & like this post. Love you Grubfam! 🙏 Thanks for the assist on filming @znicolaou & as always, thank you for making my vision come to life, @jessyfiggsfilmsphotography ❗️ #TheGrubfather #Bimini #Bahamas #BiminiBliss

❗️I’M THE FIRST AMERICAN TO EAT A HAND CRAFTED MEAL BY A @MICHELINGUIDE ⭐️ RESTAURANT IN THE AIR ✈️ Take a look at the first bite on this reel! 😋 

⚡️ This gorgeous Italian sandwich from @RezdoraNYC aboard a private @WheelsUp flight was an incredible way to get the job done ! Also, FYI… you can order Michelin Star meals on @Caviar… just saying! ✔️ 

👀 Grubfam, double tap this post and tag someone who you’d want to enjoy this experience with in the comments. 

👉 Follow me @THEGRUBFATHER for more food + travel around New York & the world. ♥️ #TheGrubfather

❗️MY DREAM COLLAB WITH THE @MICHELINGUIDE FINALLY HAPPENED: PART 1 😍 The iconic authority of the culinary arts asked me to join them on a @WheelsUp private jet to the Hamptons with @Caviar and it was a day I’ll never forget. 🦀 

⭐️ We’ll get into the all the details over a series of posts but perhaps one of the tastiest moments of the day was with The @MusketRoom, who holds a coveted star at their Manhattan location. 

😋 Executive Chef Mary Attea made the night all about King Crab. Not only did she break down the luxury crustacean in front of us but she also crafted these wildly delicious rolls crowned with caviar. Unforgettable!

🔥 CHEESE-WHEEL LOBSTER PASTA 🍝 Hit up @One10Restaurant for my brothers birthday yesterday (Happy Birthday Dom!) and this banger was on the specials menu. ✔️ Read more about it below. This spot has gotten a lot of hype and I’ll give it to them; they lived up to the word. 

👀 For this dish, they toss the fresh pasta in a cheese wheel while the lobster poaches in butter. I loved the table side aspect of this. Presentation was great too: Always love to see mounds of pasta surrounded by lobster. 😏 Also, a proper mix of tail and claw meat. Simple yet high quality ingredients and touches make this one a win. 🎯 

♥️ Grubfam, would you dig into this? Show some love by double tapping, sharing with friends & dropping a comment! Love ya. #TheGrubfather #LongIsland #Melville

🔥 TABLE-SIDE BAKED SPUMONI AT ONE OF NYC’S HOTTEST SPOTS: @CARNEMARE 🇮🇹 This whole menu was filled with amazing twists on Italian; like caviar crowned mozz sticks & a lemon basted veal Milanese that rocked my world - but dessert stole the show, literally! 🤌

👉 Spumoni is an Italian dessert that features layers of different gelatos. This version got the baked Alaska treatment with a table issue flambé - a super elevated substitute for the typical whipped cream. 

🎯 Carne Mar is a brainchild of @AndrewCarmellini & it’s DOPE. I loved every part of my meal, start to finish. It’s sometimes super tough to get a reservation and for good reason. 

⛵️Plus, it’s in the Seaport District, one of my favorite ‘hoods in Manhattan. 🎯 

♥️ Grubfam, don’t forget to double tap, share with friends who would love this & drop a comment! Much love. #TheGrubfather #Manhattan #NYC

❗️THE BEST & EASIEST TUNA SALAD RECIPE 🐟 Tbh, I was never a huge fan of tuna salad until I created this recipe which is a wild flavor ride. I’ve got the full recipe listed below and trust me: You won’t be able to eat it any other way after you try this. ✔️ Please note: The key here is HIGH QUALITY TUNA - low in mercury and preferably wild caught. 👌 

👇 GRUB TUNA SALAD 👇 
1️⃣ Open three cans of tuna, put in a big mixing bowl. 
2️⃣ Cover with four heavy teaspoons of mayonnaise, two heavy teaspoons of Dijon mustard. 
3️⃣ Drizzle in sriracha, mustard powder, garlic powder and cayenne to taste. Roughly half a teaspoon - teaspoon of each. 
4️⃣ I also use @HighNoteHotSauce’s green sauce - it’s not necessary but if you can, it kicks it up a level. 
5️⃣ Beat tuna and add ins heavy until well blended. Layer in olive oil, salt and pepper to taste. 
6️⃣ Line potato hot dog buns with bib or butter lettuce, layer in tuna fish salad. 
7️⃣ Sprinkle with red onion + scallion on top. 
8️⃣ EAT THE DANG THING! 😋 

💯 Trust me when I say this will be your new go to tuna salad recipe! Feel free to add tweaks that fit your style. 

♥️ Grubfam, show some love by liking this post, sharing with friends & dropping a comment! 

👀 Love food? Love recipes? Love travel? Hit me with a follow if it’s your first time here: @THEGRUBFATHER ✌️ Much love! #TheGrubfather #Recipes

👉 This bakery is super unique as it draws its recipes + inspiration from the owner’s Sicilian + Korean roots. That means you’re getting two styles of baking in all of their food. Fusion that works is always dreamy. 👌 

👀 Go check out my stories today to see more and stay tuned for my reel later tonight if you love donuts. Their version of Italian bombolones is… beautiful. 😏

❗️CHEESY STEAK PINWHEEL BURGER HACK 👉 Take your BBQ game up a notch by combining two classics: PINWHEELS + BURGERS 🔥 I’m always looking for ways to amp up things I love and this simple lil technique is a home-run. 

✔️ The combos you can do with this are endless but I took a steak, spinach & mozz pinwheel & stuffed it into buns I turned into garlic bread. Add some roasted red peps and bada bing, bada boom - you got something real tasty in ya hands. 😋

🦀 SOFT SHELL CRAB PASTA 🍝 @SEABAROFFICIAL is an incredible seafood restaurant and has these tasty delicacies available through the next week! 😋 

👉 Soft shell crabs are entirely edible - shell and all! I explain why in the voiceover, but in essence they’re molting their old shell and coming into their new one when they’re caught. 

💯 They will let you customize how it comes prepared but I suggest crowning them ontop of Sea Bar’s amazing creamy pink pasta! 

❗️Side note: The crabs were already ☠️ when it was cleaned in the beginning.
